{"tid":1800433,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"湯家驊: 我最敬佩孫中山","createTime":"2019-12-27T19:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T03:15:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c64c823d576e3318d9651a6f76abbfe42cadb8","tid":1800433,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:44:00.000Z","msg":"為人師表<br />\n<br />\n明報 2019-12-27 D05 | 時代 | 法政隨筆 | 湯家驊<br />\n<br />\n有人問過我，誰是我最敬佩的政治人物，我想也不想便答應該是孫中山先生。他有堅強的政治理念，鍥而不捨；不貪圖權位，為了國家好，他會退位讓賢；相信沒有太多人可以與他相比。那人又追問，那麼你最敬佩的老師是誰？我頓了一頓，一時想不出答案。沒錯，如果真的要回答，我會說是第一位在非法小學任教的老師和小學時的班主任。她們教曉我做人的道理；對同學要一視同仁，無分家境貴賤。她們教懂了我做人要謙虛，書讀愈多愈覺得自己知識淺薄。這些金石良言到今天我恐怕也難以時刻做到，但卻銘記心中。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼老師這麼重要？因為我絕對相信少年人是一張白紙。近朱者赤，近墨者黑，孟母三遷也是這個道理。我不是說什麼國教、什麼洗腦教育，我說的只是讀書是為了學懂做人的道理；若學不懂，縱是滿腹經綸、胸懷大志，也不會是一個真正的人。<br />\n<br />\n為人師表的重要性正在此中。「為人師表」這成語出自古書，師表者即榜樣也。為人師表之反義詞是誤人子弟。單是把這兩句成語放在一起，大家便明白箇中奧妙和老師的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n最近社會就是否應把政治帶入校園鬧得熱烘烘。我覺得有點可笑。做人的道理還未弄清楚，談什麼政治？談什麼理想？學懂了做人的道理，哪需害怕沒有機會認清政治對錯、理想何在？希望為人師表者撫心自問，有沒有盡到為師之道。"},{"pid":"7842702a2b599f9379ec31bc9be465ba7f828083","tid":1800433,"uid":55571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"言之無物都唔知講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c930b08c408b0c8dd342c6d9074b048eb20516e3","tid":1800433,"uid":26218,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:47:38.000Z","msg":"敬佩孫中山食親都係幼女？ <br />\n不過嗰個年代冇衰十一呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4d69843b00161ec1e6989e6c5af4f9612207ee","tid":1800433,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"我最敬佩梁天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e111d0d20413f072cfbe39ff08efb51f8d1d8101","tid":1800433,"uid":280136,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:49:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不貪圖權位，為了國家好，他會退位讓賢；相信沒有太多人可以與他相比。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n似有弦外之音wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5faf8dd7cda115e5dc3a906651bdabef7645615","tid":1800433,"uid":290393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7842702a2b599f9379ec31bc9be465ba7f828083","tid":1800433,"uid":55571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"言之無物都唔知講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:55:50.000Z","msg":"其實篇文勁有骨架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不貪圖權位，為了國家好，他會退位讓賢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢一係講緊林鄭, 一係講緊習總<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">她們教曉我做人的道理；對同學要一視同仁，無分家境貴賤。她們教懂了我做人要謙虛，書讀愈多愈覺得自己知識淺薄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢唔係講緊小學畢業果位吧? 抄頭殺頭都似. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最近社會就是否應把政治帶入校園鬧得熱烘烘。我覺得有點可笑。做人的道理還未弄清楚，談什麼政治？談什麼理想？學懂了做人的道理，哪需害怕沒有機會認清政治對錯、理想何在？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢段可以話老師太黃唔好, 亦可以話強制將政治帶入教育的愛國教育唔好. 直頭係反了 反了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbaa58cda104ee12a54b5fc07a91fca42a5ff1e","tid":1800433,"uid":10338,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:56:23.000Z","msg":"但孫中山係讀書果陣比人叫四大寇<br />\n日日講政治 點救國<br />\n最受人尊敬老師咪孫中山老師康德黎<br />\n係倫敦由清政府救返孫中山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283f67ed28a1bf5bad21aaec3168f42afbb3398e","tid":1800433,"uid":109102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"蘿莉控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdbdae6281a0e62df2b07bbac73ac4473d6a06a","tid":1800433,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a413c058b3f8873cbaabbf21a6a977835e84db27","tid":1800433,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"283f67ed28a1bf5bad21aaec3168f42afbb3398e","tid":1800433,"uid":109102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"蘿莉控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc014108a89db71e9cb6b85c16d3866af39085a","tid":1800433,"uid":65449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi8AoTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi8AoTm.png&h=c711dbd5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d07e085ef38f970cc8ed3611bf971022d6c08bc6","tid":1800433,"uid":41243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:28:30.000Z","msg":"孫中山搞大日本幼女個肚走咗去都做國父做偉人，你就做十一哥地底泥，梗係敬佩佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7626ec28580a36c44221968012b8010b409d5ab","tid":1800433,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:32:51.000Z","msg":"2個都系幼幼狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c953334c3adf8f8bed3047447ed07212c6be46","tid":1800433,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:39:05.000Z","msg":"成篇小學生中文作文程度<br />\n孫中山咪就係求學時期搞革命架囉<br />\n孫大炮個名咁響，但小學生程度應該就都未聽過，呢個要中一先識<br />\n至於蘿莉腔、不顧宋嘉澍堅決反對，強行要同宋慶齡喺東京成婚，呢個不顧世交情逆父母意嘅行為，應該點評論呢<br />\n仲有，孫中山雖然係顛覆國家政權號召暴力行為嘅反清大旗手之一，但辛亥革命成事就同佢關係不大，佢喺美國睇報紙先知雙十起義成功趕船番中國架咋<br />\n實情清室肯和平退位，主要係袁世凱倒戈，游說清室退位優待條件，如果唔係個政權交接唔會咁順利<br />\n講到尾，孫中山私生活有虧，而且係標準嘅暴力顛覆國家倡導者"},{"pid":"de9c84ccad6eabcbffc86370a01603d86c82676b","tid":1800433,"uid":78486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:50:43.000Z","msg":"最暴力嘅暴徒都好敬佩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd2dfce8e70187032b826d47056bbf2e2f8d47e","tid":1800433,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T21:53:54.000Z","msg":"華盛頓呀 孫中山死前都仲掛住死後葬係邊度 叫咩野名"},{"pid":"1c50dd3532d7b054b3a03fbd0a02e99508adb842","tid":1800433,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:00:14.000Z","msg":"孫狗唔戀棧權位都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係就唔使搞叛亂推翻北洋政府啦"},{"pid":"2468a76bfe1826e1d976c07a715c92d53c924fb1","tid":1800433,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c50dd3532d7b054b3a03fbd0a02e99508adb842","tid":1800433,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:00:14.000Z","msg":"孫狗唔戀棧權位都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係就唔使搞叛亂推翻北洋政府啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:02:42.000Z","msg":"如果唔係國民黨推翻咗北洋政府，共產黨可能唔會成事"},{"pid":"31771c8f75c782e0f75014c0071c7f02ba2caac0","tid":1800433,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:03:51.000Z","msg":"敬佩佢娶靚妹？"},{"pid":"0e848ac32102dc77d23a17d730233a12f24fd487","tid":1800433,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:04:58.000Z","msg":"大家都係衷11?"},{"pid":"2b5252964a9c22c20ab019bccb946f875837b738","tid":1800433,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T22:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/___BOUHhT090/S78LB8Z0-HI/AAAAAAAAAYM/Zop7BoojP4g/s1600/%E5%AD%AB%E5%85%88%E7%94%9F%E8%88%87%E7%BE